9a1c37f9-ad4b-438c-8082-cf637e881341.name: Disability Accomodation
9a1c37f9-ad4b-438c-8082-cf637e881341.description: The Disability Accommodation process starts with web-based requests and concludes upon processing completion. It pools accommodation requests and conducts thorough reviews for validity. Flow control manages progression. Requesters submit requests, while Reviewers evaluate and approve/reject based on validity. Notifications keep requesters informed of their request status.
